### Brokage Firm API Test Dosyası
### VS Code "REST Client" extension ile kullanılabilir

### ========== AUTH ==========

### Register - Yeni kullanıcı kayıt
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User23",
  "username": "testuser23",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "test2@test.com",
  "role": "CUSTOMER"
}

### Login - Admin girişi
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "admin123"
}

### Token'ı kaydet (login isteğinden sonra otomatik alınır)
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### ========== CUSTOMERS ==========

### Tüm müşterileri listele (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Kendi profilimi getir
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========== ASSETS ==========

### Varlıkları listele
GET http://localhost:8080/api/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Para yatır (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assets/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "customerId": 1,
    "amount": 5000
}

### Para çek
POST http://localhost:8080/api/assets/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "customerId": 1,
    "amount": 100,
    "iban": "TR123456789012345678901234"
}

### ========== ORDERS ==========

### Emirleri listele
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Bekleyen emirleri listele
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### BUY emri oluştur
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "customerId": 1,
    "assetName": "GOOG",
    "orderSide": "BUY",
    "size": 5,
    "price": 100
}

### SELL emri oluştur
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "customerId": 1,
    "assetName": "AAPL",
    "orderSide": "SELL",
    "size": 3,
    "price": 160
}

### Emir iptal et (order ID'yi değiştir)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/orders/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


